@node "history" "History"

@{u}@{b}History@{ub}@{uu}

@{b}V1.5 (August 2013)@{ub}

  - Fixed a bug in PCI ID handling that led to the wrong chipset-specific
    code being used for some cards.
  - Now uses AmigaOS-4-specific DMA functions (since the
    AmigaOS-3-compatible DMA functions are buggy).
  - Removed code for IEEE 802.11a-only chipsets (this mode is unsupported).

@{b}V1.4 (May 2013)@{ub}

  - First AmigaOS 4 release.

@endnode


